43namespace webrtc {
44class DegradedCall : public Call, private PacketReceiver {
45 public:
46 explicit DegradedCall(
47 std::unique_ptr<Call> call,
48 absl::optional<BuiltInNetworkBehaviorConfig> send_config,
49 absl::optional<BuiltInNetworkBehaviorConfig> receive_config,
50 TaskQueueFactory* task_queue_factory);
51 ~DegradedCall() override;
52
53 // Implements Call.
54 AudioSendStream* CreateAudioSendStream(
55 const AudioSendStream::Config& config) override;
56 void DestroyAudioSendStream(AudioSendStream* send_stream) override;
57
58 AudioReceiveStream* CreateAudioReceiveStream(
59 const AudioReceiveStream::Config& config) override;
60 void DestroyAudioReceiveStream(AudioReceiveStream* receive_stream) override;
61
62 VideoSendStream* CreateVideoSendStream(
63 VideoSendStream::Config config,
64 VideoEncoderConfig encoder_config) override;
65 VideoSendStream* CreateVideoSendStream(
66 VideoSendStream::Config config,
67 VideoEncoderConfig encoder_config,
68 std::unique_ptr<FecController> fec_controller) override;
69 void DestroyVideoSendStream(VideoSendStream* send_stream) override;
70
71 VideoReceiveStream* CreateVideoReceiveStream(
72 VideoReceiveStream::Config configuration) override;
73 void DestroyVideoReceiveStream(VideoReceiveStream* receive_stream) override;
74
75 FlexfecReceiveStream* CreateFlexfecReceiveStream(
76 const FlexfecReceiveStream::Config& config) override;
77 void DestroyFlexfecReceiveStream(
78 FlexfecReceiveStream* receive_stream) override;
79
80 void AddAdaptationResource(rtc::scoped_refptr<Resource> resource) override;
81
82 PacketReceiver* Receiver() override;
83
84 RtpTransportControllerSendInterface* GetTransportControllerSend() override;
85
86 Stats GetStats() const override;
87
88 const WebRtcKeyValueConfig& trials() const override;
89
90 TaskQueueBase* network_thread() const override;
91 TaskQueueBase* worker_thread() const override;
92
93 void SignalChannelNetworkState(MediaType media, NetworkState state) override;
94 void OnAudioTransportOverheadChanged(
95 int transport_overhead_per_packet) override;
96 void OnSentPacket(const rtc::SentPacket& sent_packet) override;
97
98 protected:
99 // Implements PacketReceiver.
100 DeliveryStatus DeliverPacket(MediaType media_type,
101 rtc::CopyOnWriteBuffer packet,
102 int64_t packet_time_us) override;
103
104 private:
105 class FakeNetworkPipeOnTaskQueue {
106 public:
107 FakeNetworkPipeOnTaskQueue(
108 TaskQueueFactory* task_queue_factory,
109 Clock* clock,
110 std::unique_ptr<NetworkBehaviorInterface> network_behavior);
111
112 void SendRtp(const uint8_t* packet,
113 size_t length,
114 const PacketOptions& options,
115 Transport* transport);
116 void SendRtcp(const uint8_t* packet, size_t length, Transport* transport);
117
118 void AddActiveTransport(Transport* transport);
119 void RemoveActiveTransport(Transport* transport);
120
121 private:
122 // Try to process packets on the fake network queue.
123 // Returns true if call resulted in a delayed process, false if queue empty.
124 bool Process();
125
126 Clock* const clock_;
127 rtc::TaskQueue task_queue_;
128 FakeNetworkPipe pipe_;
129 absl::optional<int64_t> next_process_ms_ RTC_GUARDED_BY(&task_queue_);
130 };
131
132 // For audio/video send stream, a TransportAdapter instance is used to
133 // intercept packets to be sent, and put them into a common FakeNetworkPipe
134 // in such as way that they will eventually (unless dropped) be forwarded to
135 // the correct Transport for that stream.
136 class FakeNetworkPipeTransportAdapter : public Transport {
137 public:
138 FakeNetworkPipeTransportAdapter(FakeNetworkPipeOnTaskQueue* fake_network,
139 Call* call,
140 Clock* clock,
141 Transport* real_transport);
142 ~FakeNetworkPipeTransportAdapter();
143
144 bool SendRtp(const uint8_t* packet,
145 size_t length,
146 const PacketOptions& options) override;
147 bool SendRtcp(const uint8_t* packet, size_t length) override;
148
149 private:
150 FakeNetworkPipeOnTaskQueue* const network_pipe_;
151 Call* const call_;
152 Clock* const clock_;
153 Transport* const real_transport_;
154 };
155
156 Clock* const clock_;
157 const std::unique_ptr<Call> call_;
158 TaskQueueFactory* const task_queue_factory_;
159
160 void SetClientBitratePreferences(
161 const webrtc::BitrateSettings& preferences) override {}
162
163 const absl::optional<BuiltInNetworkBehaviorConfig> send_config_;
164 SimulatedNetwork* send_simulated_network_;
165 std::unique_ptr<FakeNetworkPipeOnTaskQueue> send_pipe_;
166 std::map<AudioSendStream*, std::unique_ptr<FakeNetworkPipeTransportAdapter>>
167 audio_send_transport_adapters_;
168 std::map<VideoSendStream*, std::unique_ptr<FakeNetworkPipeTransportAdapter>>
169 video_send_transport_adapters_;
170
171 const absl::optional<BuiltInNetworkBehaviorConfig> receive_config_;
172 SimulatedNetwork* receive_simulated_network_;
173 std::unique_ptr<FakeNetworkPipe> receive_pipe_;
174};
175
176} // namespace webrtc
177
178#endif // CALL_DEGRADED_CALL_H_
